videos.description: J.D. King rushes for 7 yards into the end zone to put the Cowboys ahead.
videos.headline: King puts Oklahoma State on the board with TD

videos.description: Mason Rudolph completes to Marcell Ateman who makes an amazing one-handed grab.
videos.headline: Ateman makes great one-handed sideline grab

videos.description: Sam Ehlinger completes to John Burt, who somehow stays in bounds and takes it 90 yards  almost to the house.
videos.headline: Burt tiptoes down the sideline for 90-yard gain

videos.description: Sam Ehlinger runs for a 2-yard touchdown to tie Texas' game with Oklahoma State.
videos.headline: Ehlinger's TD ties the game

videos.description: Texas head coach Tom Herman is happy with his defense in the first half and doesn't believe the substituting will be an issue in the second half.
videos.headline: Herman happy they're keeping Oklahoma State out of the end zone

videos.description: Mason Rudolph finds Jalen McCleskey down the middle for 23 yards to set up Oklahoma State  for a field goal.
videos.headline: Rudolph to McCleskey puts the Cowboys in the red zone

videos.description: Mason Rudolph completes to Marcell Ateman to put the Cowboys on the 20-yard line.
videos.headline: Rudolph's 66-yard pass puts Oklahoma State in the red zone

videos.description: Sam Ehlinger's pass is intercepted in the end zone by Ramon Richards to give the Cowboys a 13-10 victory in overtime.
videos.headline: Richards' pick puts Oklahoma State on top

videos.description: Oklahoma State head coach Mike Gundy recaps on their 13-10 overtime victory over Texas.
videos.headline: Gundy: "No question this is the best game our defense has played so far"

videos.description: No. 10 Oklahoma State improves to 6-1 with a 13-10 overtime win over Texas.
videos.headline: Oklahoma State survives with OT win over Texas
